Package com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib

Class Summary
AuthToken The AuthToken class creates an authentication token using the ClientLogin API.
CaptchaInformation Represents CAPTCHA information retruned by the client login API.
DfpHttpSender DfpHttpSender acts as a custom HTTP transport layer which allows for access to the MessageContext before it is processed.
DfpService DfpService provides a class which defines a service that can be instantiated through reflection.
DfpService.V201108 The service class for v201108.

DfpService.V201208 The service class for v201208.
DfpServiceFactory The DfpServiceFactory generates service stubs with an Axis EngineConfiguration which maps the HTTP transport to the class DfpHttpSender.
DfpServiceLogger The class DfpServiceLogger allows logging of outgoing and incoming SOAP XML (DfpService) messages as API calls are executed.
DfpUser The DfpUser class contains all needed information to authenticate a user as well as generate a valid service for that user.
DfpVersion For each active version of the DoubleClick For Publishers API, there should exist a sub-class which implements the abstract class.
ServiceAccountant The ServiceAccountant class acts as an accountant for metrics extracted from the request and response from a SOAP call.
ServiceAccountantManager The ServiceAccountantManager manages all instances of ServiceAccountant by reference to the javax.xml.rpc.Service hashcode.
ServiceAccountantRecord A record for purposes of metric accounting.
 

Exception Summary
AuthTokenException An exception thrown when the ClientLogin API was unable to successfully generate a token.
